        "subject": "ORNL-29: Use bulk transfer to read IR logs",
        "message": "ORNL-29: Use bulk transfer to read IR logs\n\nWe used to read IR logs via GET_INFO RPC, this may have scalability problem\non large lustre deployment. In this patch:\n  - use bulk RPC to read IR logs;\n  - change the RPC name from GET_INFO to CONFIG_READ\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jay@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I5d79cfa9a7c75cae14ff5db7c4084ad1db548336\n"
      },
